{"tid":1633891,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉在錫節目提「反送中」 陸字幕組「自行刪除」片段","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:58:15.000Z","uid":74065,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"08f1e873e920afc87bd80d2795857469f3d1f3f6","tid":1633891,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4422/4422321.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4422%2F4422321.jpg&h=bb5e860c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲男學生選擇回答香港方面的問題。（圖／翻攝自bilibili）<br />\n<br />\n記者蔡儀潔／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n香港持續近4個月的示威運動備受國際關注，亦成為不少電視節目的題材，由韓國「國民MC」主持的綜藝節目《劉Quiz On The Block 2》就是其中之一。不過，近日大陸知名字幕組「鳳凰天使」卻將有關香港示威的片段刪除，引發大批網友討論，儘管不少人表示支持，但多數人斥責稱「真的很討厭綜藝去涉及政治」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4422/4422324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4422%2F4422324.jpg&h=f3be8868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲中間問答環節被刪去。（圖／翻攝自bilibili）<br />\n<br />\n作為劉在錫首次在tvN亮相的綜藝節目，《劉Quiz on the block》是一個以問答為主線的節目，2位主持劉在錫與曹世鎬會走訪韓國各大街頭，隨意找路人，讓他們回答由劉在錫發問的題目，成功連續答對5題的觀眾，便可獲得電視台準備的100萬韓幣獎金。<br />\n<br />\n然而在9月17日播出的節目中，慶熙大學學生梁敏錫（音譯）選擇回答與香港有關的問題，劉在錫發問，「這個物件最近在香港反送中示威中出現，被視為『反抗』的象徵物，這個東西是什麼？」<br />\n<br />\n劉在錫又提示，稱「2014年的香港示威正是以此物件命名」，梁敏錫回答了「頭盔」，但正確答案為「（黃色）雨傘」，因此該學生與獎金失諸交臂，不過仍抽到「荷葉雨傘」作安慰獎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4422/4422320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4422%2F4422320.jpg&h=77f48692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲網友對字幕組的作法持不同意見。（圖／翻攝自bilibili）<br />\n<br />\n這部綜藝節目在大陸網路上亦有播出，由「鳳凰天使」提供簡體中文字幕，不過有網友發現，9月17日節目的片段遭剪輯，令梁敏錫沒有玩遊戲便直接跳到抽安慰獎環節。有看過完整節目的網民則推測，「鳳凰天使」為了能通過大陸網站審查和避免引起爭議，所以刪除與香港示威有關的節目內容。<br />\n<br />\n此事引發大量討論。有網民不滿「鳳凰天使」剪去香港片段，「怕啥呢」、「沒必要吧。。。也要聽聽別人的想法啊」、「自作主張剪掉了？對自己多不自信都不敢被討論？」、「還是覺得沒必要剪切，是真實問了的問題而已」、「這都能剪也是對自己太不自信了」。<br />\n<br />\n但也有人支持字幕組，「不剪掉可能我們連這集都看不到了」、「不剪過得了審嘛小可愛們」、「見了就說明不適合中國觀眾 何苦自己去找來受罪」，亦有人指責節目，「問這種問題，一綜藝節目也過管閒事」、「真的很討厭綜藝去涉及政治，你們以什麼立場來談呢」。"},{"pid":"52479842b5cd97f2d6836d9d3cfaecf707792982","tid":1633891,"uid":167880,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:41:31.000Z","msg":"國民主持人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9c516848e4dfd9dfa9f5ea082b600123aedaa0","tid":1633891,"uid":240447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:41:32.000Z","msg":"仲以為大陸人完全唔知香港發生緊咁大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df7f3a59dca4081d92c8d46a82fe0d8bd128ea0","tid":1633891,"uid":235015,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:41:32.000Z","msg":"又限韓又要睇<br />\n支那人真係好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3284b83f482e817b18706f0bb43105a7f85716a","tid":1633891,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:42:40.000Z","msg":"on9大陸狗"},{"pid":"d33bd387222dea838accbf1fcd209e40d7c4fc7b","tid":1633891,"uid":74065,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:43:06.000Z","msg":"另一個字幕最中意自行加上中國香港同中國台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6d3d63cff04ac1f27c37168569c1e27a770d8a","tid":1633891,"uid":40520,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"無限挑戰一堆政治野<br />\n個時班人咪又係狂追<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8dc29354f5a288b6fb136a06841afb08048a1c","tid":1633891,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb6d3d63cff04ac1f27c37168569c1e27a770d8a","tid":1633891,"uid":40520,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"無限挑戰一堆政治野<br />\n個時班人咪又係狂追<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:13.000Z","msg":"朴明秀串9D大陸狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c267d8e759966eca64de0c544d15437f8109e16f","tid":1633891,"uid":35087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:14.000Z","msg":"人哋拍俾你睇咩"},{"pid":"7cd85487376e03f2c62da1afc102aaa26fcca14e","tid":1633891,"uid":46435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:30.000Z","msg":"劉在錫真係神級.."},{"pid":"ac184d0921bdea813fdf5526fbb1b2654a6211b3","tid":1633891,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:06.000Z","msg":"呢條咁普通都要剪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec968c87e4bc69b9789c7fc243109a265fa0721","tid":1633891,"uid":1049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:15.000Z","msg":"字幕組唔係老翻野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老翻都要審查？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729cc2f88e8ac48ac4f18cd3a9829875439df8f5","tid":1633891,"uid":240608,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"咁又真係得大陸會做字幕喎，無計<br />\n<br />\n我唔見香港人做 日韓字幕<br />\n<br />\n市場太細"},{"pid":"6e7b434d55aadb0326da9835032edf2f24c1e484","tid":1633891,"uid":208486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:54:51.000Z","msg":"大陸狗真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147e02bbd87b330854b067ee38162f88bfde20e5","tid":1633891,"uid":42011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ec968c87e4bc69b9789c7fc243109a265fa0721","tid":1633891,"uid":1049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:15.000Z","msg":"字幕組唔係老翻野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老翻都要審查？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:58:15.